Package org.neo4j.kernel.impl.store

Class StoreAccess

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.store.StoreAccess
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AccessStatsKeepingStoreAccess
    public class StoreAccess
extends Object
    Not thread safe (since DiffRecordStore is not thread safe), intended for single threaded use. Make sure to call initialize() after constructor has been run.

    • Method Detail

      • initialize

        public StoreAccess initialize()
        This method exists since wrapStore(RecordStore) might depend on the existence of a variable that gets set in a subclass' constructor after this constructor of StoreAccess has been executed. I.e. a correct creation of a StoreAccess instance must be the creation of the object plus a call to this method.
        Returns:
        this
